{{Quote|I absolutely love 'Star Wars'! When I saw the very first 'Star Wars', I can still remember the feeling I had when I walked out of the cinema&hellip; I had this feeling of &hellip; sadness? &hellip; disappointment?&hellip; I'm not sure if those are the correct words but I had sort of an empty feeling because I knew that the adventure (for the time being) was over and all of those cool characters and settings wouldn't be part of my tomorrow. I wanted more! So being part of the 'Star Wars' games was an honor. Playing Rhys Dallows, the only human pilot, made me feel like I was Luke Skywalker. What fun!|Darren Scott|<ref name="Wordpress">{{WordPress|subdomain=mattjhorn|url=2011/08/18/darren-scott-the-rig-2010/|name=Matt J. Horn|text=Darren Scott – (The Rig – 2010).|archivedate=20260305114811}}</ref>}}
'''Darren Scott''' (born [[November 24]], [[1960s#1965|1965]]) voiced [[Rhys Dallows]] in [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']] and ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''.

